snippet.title: Diabolic - Official Trailer (2026) Elizabeth Cullen, John Kim, Mia Challis
snippet.description:
Take a look at the Official Trailer for Diabolic, a horror film distributed by Brainstorm Media. Witness a woman in search of a cure who ends up becoming a sinister target in Diabolic, in theaters and On Demand on February 20.

A woman must return to the fundamentalist compound where she was raised after she is haunted by the vengeful spirit of a cursed witch.

Diabolic stars Elizabeth Cullen, John Kim, Mia Challis, Robin Goldsworthy, Genevieve Mooy, and more. The film is directed by Daniel J. Phillips and written by Mike Harding, Daniel J. Phillips, and Ticia Madsen.

Diabolic is in theaters and On Demand on February 20.
